    "note": "Past continuous revision (was/were + -ing; interrupted action with when + past simple; simultaneous with while; was/were agreement; error classes incl. stative-verb trap). 36 vocab + 55 grammar, full v1 parity (floor 40 → 55 items / 9 formats — largest grammar set so far). 4 verify lenses clean after fixes: cp.003 reframed to past (was present-framed, which made the present-continuous distractor defensibly correct); mt.001 pairs pronoun-tied for uniqueness (two While-clauses were swappable); ec.005/ec.010 set strict (single-char spelling fixes); sb.001/sb.002 + tr.001 reversed-order / 'learning' answer variants added; granted fungi/something/walking/learning/wind/ing (harvesting-gap words + -ing forms inside lang:de-prompt carriers that validate's field-scoping misses — the level-gloss lens correctly caught 'wind'); relabeled richtig/falsch group-sort → ✓/✗; pipe-joined mc.006's 2-blank combinations; raised sb.003 chip budget to 12; reworded 'Zustands-Verb'→'want und like beschreiben einen Zustand' ('Verb' banned in prompts). The 2 gloss audits (blow/send, prompt-scoped) are correct; 38 translation audits accurate both directions. 2 defensible enToDe warns (Catholic / interfere slash-variants trip the homograph heuristic; German is correct). Validate green."
